              <circle cx="32" cy="34" r="3" stroke-width="0.8" />
              <circle cx="32" cy="34" r="0.8" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="brand-word">sigil</span>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-tagline">Closed-loop shipping for coding agents. You audit — not operate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Product</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/how/">How it works</a></li>
          <li><a href="/quickstart/">Quickstart</a></li>
          <li><a href="/how/#invariants">Invariants</a></li>
          <li><a href="/how/#trust">Trust model</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
